    <note id="fs-id1167063512324" class="learning-objectives">
<label/>
<title>Section Learning Objectives</title>
<para id="fs-id1167066960118">By the end of this section, you will be able to do the following:</para>
<list id="fs-id1167067083238">
<item>Explain the meaning of slope in position vs. time graphs</item>
<item>Solve problems using position vs. time graphs</item>
</list>
    </note>
<note id="fs-id1167067127805" class="os-teacher">
        <title>Teacher Support</title>
        <para id="fs-id1167066770435">The learning objectives in this section will help your students master the following standards:</para><list id="fs-id1167066845499">
