          (4) Science concepts. The student knows and applies the laws governing motion in a variety of situations. The student is expected to:
        <list id="fs-id1167066793729"><item><span>(A)</span> <span>generate and interpret graphs and charts describing different types of motion, including the use of real-time technology such as motion detectors or photogates.</span></item>

        </list></item>
        </list>
